  "full_path": "do lowest-losing-bid-prediction-subject-details create",
  "description": "Create a lowest losing bid prediction subject detail.",
  "permissions": "Allowed for admins and broker admins for the related prediction subject (policy delegates to prediction_subject).",
  "side_effects": "Creates a detail record and triggers updates on the related prediction subject (domain reset and actual/lowest bid recalculation from bid details or bid amount). If bid_details are provided and a broker exists, it syncs bidders and prediction subject bids from the bid details and creates a self-bidder prediction_subject_bid.",
  "validation_notes": "--prediction-subject is required. prediction_subject must have kind \"lowest_losing_bid\". Only one detail per prediction_subject is allowed (unique index). bid-details must be valid JSON; each element amount must be numeric if present. prediction_subject relationship is create-only.",
